) 18... Nxf4 (18... O-O 19. Be3 Rd8 20. Qa6 $18) 19. Qxd7+ Kf8 20. Re4 (20. Bc6
{makes it even easier for White} Qd8 21. g3 Qxd7 22. Bxd7 Ng6 $18) 20... a6 (
