}) 13. exd4 Rc8 14. Qb1 Qa6 {White king safety dropped} 15. Bf1 {White
threatens to win material: Bf1xa6} Qb6 {White king safety improved} 16. Bg2 Na5
17. O-O Bd6 18. Bxd6 Qxd6 19. f4 Nc4 20. Nxc4 Rxc4 21. Qd3 a6 22. Rae1 O-O 23.
Kh1 (23. f5 gxf5 24. gxf5 Re8 $11) 23... b5 24. a3 Rfc8 25. f5 gxf5 26. gxf5
