Gc5d4,Gd7d4] The pressure on the isolated pawn grows} h6 {Prevents intrusion
on g5} 25. b4 $4 (25. Rd2 $142 $11 {had to be tried to avoid defeat}) 25...
Bxb4 $19 26. Nxd4 $2 (26. Rg1 Bc4 27. Qe4 $19) 26... Bc4 27. Qg4 (27. Qe4 {
hardly improves anything} Bxf1 28. Rxf1 Qc4 $19) 27... Bxf1 28. e6 (28. Rxf1 {
does not solve anything} Qxe5 29. c3 Bd6 $19) 28... Bxg2+ $1 {it's all over}
